Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences across all cases
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities

Name: Percentage of variants that include SW-Awaiting AE Assignment immediately after SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Number of times SW-Awaiting AE Assignment is directly followed by SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences that eventually lead to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in variants that result in an acceptance (e.g., followed by SW-EIC Accept or RW-EIC Accept)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment relative to the frequency of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Number of cases where SW-Awaiting AE Assignment appears more than once
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities

Name: Percentage of variants containing SW-Awaiting AE Assignment that proceed to reviewer assignment activities (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment compared to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences that are not followed by any reviewer-related activity within 30 days
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all cases

Name: Number of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment events that occur after a plagiarism check (Plagiarism Originality Report Completed)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in the context of initial submissions versus revised submissions (e.g., following Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation vs. Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in cases that later involve editor reassignment (e.g., Assign a Different Editor or Unassign Editor)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'Assign a Different Editor' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment that precedes at least one instance of SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Number of variants where SW-Awaiting AE Assignment is skipped entirely
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' does not occur

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment occurrences that are part of high-duration process variants (performance > 1,000,000 seconds)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in cases that ultimately end with Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist or Manuscript is Withdrawn
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment that occurs within 24 hours of SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'
